question.en:
You are testing a React component that fetches user data from an API and displays it. Which testing approach would you choose and why?
jsx
function UserProfile({ userId }) {
  const [user, setUser] = useState(null);
  useEffect(() => {
    fetchUser(userId).then(setUser);
  }, [userId]);
  return user ? <div>{user.name}</div> : <div>Loading...</div>;
}

What is the most appropriate testing level for verifying this component works end-to-end?

